# Example Project

## Overview
This is an example project demonstrating the AI Context Standard CLI tool.

## Architecture
The project follows a simple modular architecture:
- `aicontext.py` - Main CLI tool implementation
- `setup.py` - Installation configuration
- `examples/` - Example .aicontext files

## Coding Standards
- Use type hints for all Python functions
- Follow PEP 8 style guidelines
- Include docstrings for all public functions
- Use meaningful variable names

## Dependencies
- PyYAML for YAML parsing
- markdown for Markdown processing
- Python 3.7+ required

## Context Hints
This tool is designed to work alongside existing AI tools without requiring changes to existing .aicontext files.